972 /* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
973  -- DMA Peripheral Access Layer
974  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
975 
982 typedef struct {
983  uint8_t RESERVED_0[256];
984  struct { /* offset: 0x100, array step: 0x10 */
985  __IO uint32_t SAR;
986  __IO uint32_t DAR;
987  union { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
988  __IO uint32_t DSR_BCR;
989  struct { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
990  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
991  __IO uint8_t DSR;
992  } DMA_DSR_ACCESS8BIT;
993  };
994  __IO uint32_t DCR;
995  } DMA[4];
996 } DMA_Type, *DMA_MemMapPtr;

1000  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- */

1012 #define DMA_DAR_COUNT 4
1013 #define DMA_DSR_BCR_REG(base,index) ((base)->DMA[index].DSR_BCR)
1014 #define DMA_DSR_BCR_COUNT 4
1015 #define DMA_DSR_REG(base,index) ((base)->DMA[index].DMA_DSR_ACCESS8BIT.DSR)
1016 #define DMA_DSR_COUNT 4
1017 #define DMA_DCR_REG(base,index) ((base)->DMA[index].DCR)
1018 #define DMA_DCR_COUNT 4

6029 typedef struct {
6030  __IO uint32_t SC;
6031  __IO uint32_t CNT;
6032  __IO uint32_t MOD;
6033  struct { /* offset: 0xC, array step: 0x8 */
6034  __IO uint32_t CnSC;
6035  __IO uint32_t CnV;
6036  } CONTROLS[6];
6037  uint8_t RESERVED_0[20];
6038  __IO uint32_t STATUS;
6039  uint8_t RESERVED_1[48];
6040  __IO uint32_t CONF;
6041 } TPM_Type, *TPM_MemMapPtr;
